the unprecedented access to data and

00:04:16.210 --> 00:04:20.840
analytics are driving societal
change at a spectacular pace.

00:04:20.840 --> 00:04:24.100
The scope, scale, and
ubiquity of these technologies

00:04:24.100 --> 00:04:27.290
are revolutionizing every
sector of our economy

00:04:27.290 --> 00:04:30.220
including finance,
healthcare, transportation,

00:04:30.220 --> 00:04:34.169
energy, manufacturing,
education, and yes, the arts.

00:04:35.330 --> 00:04:40.210
The trail blazing work of our faculty and 
students has position CMU at

00:04:40.210 --> 00:04:43.820
the leading edge of human progress.

00:04:43.820 --> 00:04:48.940
There's never been a more exciting time to
engage in research and work that matters.

00:04:50.150 --> 00:04:55.081
The potential for profound impact is
extraordinary and we at CMU have a long

00:04:55.081 --> 00:05:00.495
tradition of excellence in our bold
visual arts, music, and theater programs

00:05:00.495 --> 00:05:02.874
and we continue to define and

00:05:02.874 --> 00:05:08.441
manage the space where our humanity
intersects with technology.

00:05:08.441 --> 00:05:13.100
CMU not only embraces the new
paradigms we define them.

00:05:13.100 --> 00:05:16.392
Our university recruits diverse
perspectives and ideas

00:05:16.392 --> 00:05:20.290
to advance human knowledge and
pursue new modes of human expression.

00:05:21.380 --> 00:05:25.600
Here at CMU we dismantle the silos
restricting forward momentum

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:29.710
and we help people from all
walks of life to succeed.

00:05:31.070 --> 00:05:34.500
When we consider ideas from
across the grand spectrum

00:05:34.500 --> 00:05:38.230
in a culture of civil discourse,
we all win.

00:05:38.230 --> 00:05:40.870
The things that make our community unique

00:05:40.870 --> 00:05:42.850
have never been more
valuable than they are now.

00:05:44.940 --> 00:05:47.600
Now the future of education
in the 21st century

00:05:47.600 --> 00:05:50.860
will depend upon breaking
down disciplinary silos.

00:05:50.860 --> 00:05:56.410
It will be forged by diverse minds coming
together in learning and research.

00:05:57.430 --> 00:06:01.510
As an institution grounded in
relentless creativity and

00:06:01.510 --> 00:06:05.230
driven by fearless entrepreneurial spirit,

00:06:05.230 --> 00:06:09.340
Carnegie Mellon University knows
how to do this better than anyone.

00:06:10.740 --> 00:06:14.809
Education is the key to staying
ahead of the fast moving current.

00:06:15.820 --> 00:06:20.010
To make the most of opportunities that
lie ahead, we must be willing to disrupt

00:06:20.010 --> 00:06:25.010
the system of higher education itself,
and to do that we need a bold leader.

00:06:26.500 --> 00:06:30.500
The single greatest responsibility of
our Board of trustees, thank you so

00:06:30.500 --> 00:06:35.519
many of you for being here, is to select
a president who can guide our university.

00:06:37.020 --> 00:06:40.190
Dr. Farnam Jahanian is the right
leader at the right time

00:06:40.190 --> 00:06:42.320
to guide our great university forward.

00:06:43.850 --> 00:06:48.590
A prominent scientist,
creative entrepreneur, public servant and

00:06:48.590 --> 00:06:53.100
esteemed educator, Farnam Jahanian
brings the experience, passion, and

00:06:53.100 --> 00:06:55.910
leadership necessary to steer CMU.

00:06:57.410 --> 00:07:02.190
Each of us has a role in his
success here as we charge in with

00:07:02.190 --> 00:07:07.890
the fantastic work of magnifying the
societal impact of scientific discovery

00:07:07.890 --> 00:07:11.250
emphasizing our leadership and
creative expression and

00:07:11.250 --> 00:07:14.860
building the skills students need for
a lifetime of learning.

00:07:16.160 --> 00:07:18.740
I ask all of you, and each of you,

00:07:18.740 --> 00:07:23.540
to join me in supporting him, in his
efforts, to meet this strategic vision.

