Whether as a world-renowned
computer scientist, a passionate,

00:17:07.507 --> 00:17:11.295
successful entrepreneur,
a tireless public servant or

00:17:11.295 --> 00:17:15.060
a world-class leader in higher education.

00:17:15.060 --> 00:17:18.310
And, oh by the way, just an incredible,
incredible human being.

