00:18:28.390 --> 00:18:32.080
has a talent, a true talent for bringing
people together and breaking down walls.

00:18:33.380 --> 00:18:38.230
Farnam is also a leader with impeccable
integrity and the highest of character.

00:18:38.230 --> 00:18:44.330
He conducts himself with grace, and
dignity, and thoughtfulness, and warmth.

00:18:44.330 --> 00:18:47.000
There is no question,
no question Farnam will guide this

00:18:47.000 --> 00:18:49.920
institution into the future and
accelerate its impact on the world.

