Now, this torch has been held by many,

00:18:58.728 --> 00:19:02.420
many great leaders throughout
Carnegie Mellon's very rich history

00:19:02.420 --> 00:19:04.780
and there have been so
many accomplishments and so

00:19:04.780 --> 00:19:05.880
many historic milestones.

