a technical school in 1900,

00:19:11.150 --> 00:19:12.790
individuals of great character and

00:19:12.790 --> 00:19:18.430
honor have taken the reigns of leadership
of this very prestigious institution

00:19:18.430 --> 00:19:22.888
and each of them have led with courage and vision.

